"48:15:4" : {s: 48, a: 15, w: 4, r: "طلق", t: "ٱنطَلَقْتُمْ", l: "ٱنطَلَقَ", lc: 9, tl: "inṭalaqtum", lb: "চলা, গমন করা",e: "you set forth", b: "তোমরা পৌছবে", i: "kamu berangkat", f: 1, rm: "to be free from bond, be divorced, be repudiated. talaaq - divorce. taallaqa (vb. 2) - to divorce/quit/leave. mutallaqatun - divorced woman. intalaqa - to start doing something, depart, set out in doing something, go ones way, be free or loose.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٧ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect 7th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(VII)", deg: "2", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "يَنطَلِقُ"},
